#    - Port 8080 (Reverb WebSocket)
#    - Port 5432 (PostgreSQL, if database is on this server)
#
# 4. After updating IP addresses:
#    - Run: php artisan config:clear
#    - Run: npm run build (to rebuild with new VITE_REVERB_HOST)
